Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.09,0:22:24.68,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad0\be1}面向未來　擁抱夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:28.65,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad0\be1}下定決心　仰望天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.65,0:22:34.73,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad0\be1}用我的翅膀跨越未來
