Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.63,0:22:42.57,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad0\be1}我宣佈　絕對love !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:48.52,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad0\be1}閃亮的季節漸漸逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:53.24,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad0\be1}紀念照裡的妳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.24,0:22:57.17,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad0\be1}是那一成不變的　困惑的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.74,0:23:04.03,ED_TW,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad0\be1}溫柔地　溫暖地　讓我淚水盈眶
