Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依然收拾的很乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道妳會到這裡來  薰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我並不想以這個形式和妳見面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了  葵  紫穗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說這種話的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生為了找妳而去了紐約
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我是來見葵和紫穗的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也猜到妳們倆會在這裡埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳以為我們會跟妳走嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳真的以為我們會成為P.A.N.D.R.A的同伴  和普通人戰鬥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明抗ESP裝置還在起作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周圍全是瓦礫  這樣子沒辦法瞬移
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們倆都會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們從小就是好友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼好友啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要妳們知道我看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通人在背地裡都對超能力者做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能被她煽動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙已經不是以前的薰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,證據就是她這麼長時間裡居然都沒說出一個大叔笑話來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是變了  而是改正了這個不良習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一直能像那個時候一樣的話  那是多麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  真好  新生真是可愛的不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全無法想像在四五年過後會擁有大人般的巨乳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這是什麼大叔品味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正這傢伙從小時候開始就是這副德性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我們也五年級了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不代表有什麼會改變…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊  完全沒有成長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳給我趕快把這壞毛病改掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  薰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對教育不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  皆本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜班結束了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.27,0:04:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是慶祝我們升五年級吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？  呃…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得太樸素了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是普通的點心啊  有什麼不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升五年級有什麼好專門慶祝的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慶祝一下又有什麼關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有愛啊  愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意見這麼大的話那就還我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過明天會好好慶祝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真纏人啊  都說了不會慶祝的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛上完夜班  所以要去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本那傢伙算什麼意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  管理官也確實說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們也不會一直是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突破口是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何我都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保護她們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲  三位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜升五年級
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又成長了一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兵部少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得跟平時有點不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不很明顯嗎  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那幫傢伙圍上來要我穿成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  我才不要裝年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學生服不是裝年輕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管了  給我穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外因為其他兩位對我懷有戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我今天裝了大量的限制器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的我和普通人沒有任何區別  是手無寸鐵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過以防萬一  我雇用了保鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指的是他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  桃太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是個值得依靠的真男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我是站在楚楚可憐的幼女這邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要妳們有意思的話  我隨時都可以幹掉這個LOLI控
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀  真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上把他幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:06:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不帶他來比較好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣呢？  這樣就放心了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無論如何都想和妳們一起慶祝妳們的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會陪我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微觀察一下情況也是無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要帶我們去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  坐上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰  葵  紫穗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好地方是…這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是普通的遊樂園嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜歡嗎  難得我全包下來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  只是覺得太過普通了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  這裡是普通的遊玩場所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們並不普通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的設施對ESP有很多限制的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們沒有在這種地方玩過吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:07:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽  我也想和姐姐一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要和媽媽一起留在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在意  這不是妳的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那裡玩的人都會被廁所裡的手給拖進去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身上的錢全都會被搶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  要從哪個開始玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說  其實我也是第一次來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要玩那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去遊戲中心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要慌不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還拿著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能還回去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易悄悄地拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  不要這麼不懂得變通嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Children{\i}   解禁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉囉轉囉  旋轉木馬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管接下來會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不講客套
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:09:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在遊樂園  B.A.B.E.L和P.A.N.D.R.A也握手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對可憐{\i1}Children{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過和我們平常做的不是差不多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼試試那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就會覺得很爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬移影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼…眼睛花了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一秒敲了8～10下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生可能會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天他還在睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳真酷啊  不好玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遊樂園是很好玩  不過和你在一起就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起和你在一起  我們更喜歡待在皆本先生身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約會的時候談別的男人不大好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:09:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女帝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這是什麼叫法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介  我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡現在沒有工作人員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吃點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們想去哪我都會帶妳們去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個女人的弱點原來是這方面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我記得冰箱裡有皆本先生做好的晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰  真不愧是女王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我們馬上去做準備  你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是吵醒家裡的人就不好了  要安靜點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  好久沒來這裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  我剛說了要安靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那個加熱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:10:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  奶油濃湯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要放上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烏賊墨汁之類的就放過我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,イカスミとかは、勘弁してよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子們  3月是彌生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,よい子のみんな、3月は、彌生、だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:13.88,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,彌生是日本農曆3月，也指西元前4世紀到西元後3世紀的彌生時代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵  這就是妳們平常吃的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是平民化的  樸素的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為皆本先生的料理技術是很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意見那就回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  別生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是很有家庭的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他帶回家還是有點做的太過火了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們倆也沒反對嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是順勢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們境遇很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒從不二子小姐那聽說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和妳們一樣大的時候也是特殊超能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陸軍特殊超能力部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在的B.A.B.E.L的前身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是伊號爺爺的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介原來也是同伴的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過任務的內容和現在不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了社會為了國家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們積極了運用自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  為什麼事到如今說這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後來戰爭爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們成為了兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我依舊相信這是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我還有同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且信任他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿  看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳有在看嗎  不二子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣擊墜數首位…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不二子小姐？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我被擊中了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上回母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  我沒辦法瞬間移動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念動力也已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我帶妳回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳可以自己止血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊  當時超能力者還是少數
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的力量也是有極限的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒法改變世界的趨勢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場戰爭是我們輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只剩無條件投降一條路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有能用的戰力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超能力部隊除了你之外也全都負傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人也能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少敵人的下一輪轟炸…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來的命運是註定的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,註定？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰敗  復興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及接下來的毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡的海豚的腦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在沖繩成功回收了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分析的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現伊九號對我們隱瞞了部分預知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大戰後超能力者會不斷增加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後你會成為他們的領導者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將世界毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們創造出像你這樣的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不能被佔領軍知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類之間的戰爭已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往後的敵人——超能力者也要趁現在解決
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往後的敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們終究…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下你可以連升兩級
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他同伴現在也光榮戰死…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是怪物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是  在那之後我有了複數的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們沒在吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是肚子餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽這種事情誰還吃得下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那個人像皆本一樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介也一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一發生衝突  妳認為他會站在哪一邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我的眼鏡放哪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣什麼也看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得是在這附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  妳做了什麼好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本想拿給妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  沒這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少佐  你那樣簡直就像是偷情的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  有誰在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先…先別管這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:15:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從浴室裡傳出紫穗的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生  救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  紫穗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫穗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.84,0:16:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒為請我吃飯一事道謝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向主夫問好  這是小費
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像這樣  我的限制器全部都能解除
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來想趁他發現我的時候對他施加催眠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果…如果妳敢對皆本出手的話  我絕不原諒妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才乖乖地等待時機到來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過作弄作弄他是可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和其他普通人是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從他來了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的一切都改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:17:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們和妳們的能力我都喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向我開槍的那個男人也曾說過類似的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙全是一丘之貉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒騙妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想妳們…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事是不可能發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  真是不懂事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來光是嘴上說妳是不會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我退下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嗎  放任我不管的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳重視的人就可能會遭遇危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念動 腳跟落下技
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念動 鐵槌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念動  殘像百烈拳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過如此嗎  成長了的妳的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念動 無敵之盾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點程度的話  是沒辦法保護妳最喜歡的皆本的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵和紫穗也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有妳現在重視的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去妳會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,念動  風剪浪影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:30.64,Eng,NTP,0,0,0,,Scissors Wave
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰  剛才這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將力量壓縮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是京介教給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  如果你敢對皆本出手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成長超過了我的預想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介  你是故意惹她哭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本沒這打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘了  薰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正傷害妳的人不是我  而是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再一起玩吧  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京介這…笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成為妳們的負責人滿一周年的日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  你還記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰  這麼晚了妳究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才要慶祝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預備用的眼鏡  在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  就沒有什麼禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然稱不上是慶祝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過作為紀念…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音樂盒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.88,0:20:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曲子是「夢幻曲」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有相框啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我們明天一起去拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要明天  現在就拍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要現在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全身溼答答的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為  明天會怎麼樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也無法預料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就先聽聽妳怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過之後的行動妳可別抱有太大的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春天是初始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春眠不覺曉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去一下政府機關
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午就會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲  能幫我交給{\i1}Children{\i} 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你好像不打算慶祝她們的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不開槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個藏起來的危險東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有所自覺吧  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己現在有多麼的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:21:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管掙扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來在一刻刻地逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆本
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,下回的絕對可憐{\i1}Children{\i} 是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一個人看家？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,還不知道會造成什麼損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.00,0:23:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在傷好之前好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.84,0:23:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  妳不用來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.15,0:23:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  女王  很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.96,0:23:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我才不想借助妳這種人的力量...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是要和黑色幽靈戰鬥是需要妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.88,0:23:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對可憐{\i1}Children{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.55,0:24:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第48話  「理力騷然！看不見的威脅」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.76,0:24:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對可憐  所以不會輸！
